snippet.title: Brush along with Pokémon in Pokémon Smile!
snippet.description:
Get ready to show us your pearly whites! 

Introducing #PokemonSmile, a free app designed to provide a fun toothbrushing experience for even the tiniest Trainers—available today on iOS and Android!

https://bit.ly/2USa8y6

Official site: http://www.pokemon.com 
Shop: http://www.pokemoncenter.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/Pokemon 
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/Pokemon 
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/pokemon
